-- Hugo Chavez Sees ‘Slight Improvement,’ Villegas Says
-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 2012-12-24T21:30:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-24/hugo-chavez-sees-slight-improvement-villegas-says.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez  is
experiencing a “slight improvement” in his condition after
cancer surgery in Cuba, Information Minister Ernesto Villegas
said.  Chavez has been communicating with family members and
analyzing the results of regional elections held Dec. 16,
Villegas said in a national address broadcast on radio and
television.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
